<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.0>intro-&gt;[introprefix]、[introsuffix] 在 [place_name]、[place_adjective] 定居点和 [place_summary]，幸存者发现了脆弱的脚部老旧。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.0>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.1>introprefix-&gt;炸弹落下，老旧 世界崩溃后</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.1>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.10>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;饥饿席卷了他们的定居点，迫使人们绝望地走出已知的边界去寻找食物。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.10>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.11>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;辐射风暴席卷了大地，毒害了地球和心灵，考验着他们的决心。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.11>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.12>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;变异的野兽和扭曲的恐怖潜伏在黑暗中，威胁着每一步。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.12>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.13>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;幸存者之间的恐惧和猜疑日益加深，内部冲突破坏了他们的团结。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.13>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.14>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;老旧 战争的幽灵在 老旧 化的城市中回响，敌对派系在这些城市中争夺以 [place_powerCenter] 为中心的摇摇欲坠的权力。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.14>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.15>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;由辐射和污秽产生的荒地疾病席卷了整个社区，夺走了年轻人和 老旧 的生命​​，而且看不到治愈的方法。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.15>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.16>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;不稳定的水源要么干涸，要么中毒，迫使人们踏上危险的旅程，前往遥远、未知的绿洲。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.16>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.17>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;天空被火山灰和风暴燃烧，遮蔽了阳光，大地寒冷到了骨子里c老旧。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.17>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.18>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;敌对战帮发动了残酷的袭击，夷平了农场和村庄，驱散了家庭，瓦解了脆弱的联盟。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.18>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.19>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;老旧 世界技术摇摇欲坠和崩溃，幸存者只能冒着巨大的风险从废品中拼凑出武器和工具。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.19>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.2>introprefix-&gt;核火灾之后</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.2>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.20>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;一种潜伏的、非自然的威胁——被科学扭曲的变种人变得疯狂——的低语在人们中传播了恐惧和偏执。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.20>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.21>response-&gt;[responseprefix], [responsesuffix] 在 [place_community] 这样的中心周围，[place_adjective] 人民聚集在一起，其中包括维持脆弱和平的 [place_job] 人。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.21>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.22>responseprefix-&gt;有些人转向 老旧 方式</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.22>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.23>responseprefix-&gt;领袖崛起——军阀</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.23>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.24>responseprefix-&gt;他们与邻近团体建立了脆弱的联盟</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.24>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.25>responseprefix-&gt;其他人则拥抱残酷的生存主义</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.25>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.26>responseprefix-&gt;宗教崇拜和奇怪的新信仰蓬勃发展</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.26>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.27>responseprefix-&gt;熟练的拾荒者和工程师重新利用 老旧 技术</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.27>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.28>responsesuffix-&gt;以部落仪式和祖先精神为指导。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.28>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.29>responsesuffix-&gt;选举产生的议会——每个议会都声称对自己的人民拥有权威。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.29>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.3>introprefix-&gt;第一次世界大战留下的伤痕比沙漠和废墟s更深</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.3>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.30>responsesuffix-&gt;交易知识、武器和希望。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.30>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.31>responsesuffix-&gt;先发制人，对敌人毫不留情。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.31>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.32>responsesuffix-&gt;在混乱中提供意义。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.32>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.33>responsesuffix-&gt;保卫和维持他们的家园。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.33>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.34>transformation-&gt;[transformationprefix], [transformationsuffix] 他们的大厅，就像[place_powerCenter]一样，成为混乱中秩序的象征。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.34>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.35>transformationprefix-&gt;随着时间的推移，他们的习俗变成了法律</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.35>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.36>transformationprefix-&gt;最初是分散的幸存者成长为一支强大的力量</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.36>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.37>transformationprefix-&gt;他们的旗帜在战场和议会大厅中升起</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.37>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.38>transformationprefix-&gt;有些人在 废墟 城市的 废墟 定居</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.38>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.39>transformationprefix-&gt;苦难的伤痕烙印在他们身上</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.39>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.4>introprefix-&gt;当文明堕落时</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.4>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.40>transformationprefix-&gt;传奇围绕着他们的领袖而成长</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.40>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.41>transformationsuffix-&gt;仪式和牢不可破的誓言。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.41>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.42>transformationsuffix-&gt;整个荒原都令人畏惧和尊敬。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.42>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.43>transformationsuffix-&gt;团结和力量的象征。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.43>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.44>transformationsuffix-&gt;将衰败变成希望的堡垒。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.44>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.45>transformationsuffix-&gt;造就了一支永远不会向墙外的恐怖低头的民族。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.45>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.46>transformationsuffix-&gt;火光下的故事 t老旧 激励子孙后代。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.46>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.47>legacy-&gt;[legacyprefix], [legacysuffix] 曾经只是 [place_name] 的一群幸存者，现在他们成为了坚韧的证明。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.47>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.48>legacyprefix-&gt;现在</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.48>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.49>legacyprefix-&gt;从破碎的开始</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.49>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.5>introsuffix-&gt;分散的幸存者在受辐射的废墟中勉强度日。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.5>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.50>legacyprefix-&gt;他们的故事是关于韧性的故事</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.50>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.51>legacyprefix-&gt;虽然废弃物很严重</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.51>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.52>legacyprefix-&gt;随着 老旧 世界的消失</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.52>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.53>legacyprefix-&gt;时间会审判他们</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.53>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.54>legacysuffix-&gt;他们的名字在荒原上回响，是盟友的灯塔，也是敌人的警告。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.54>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.55>legacysuffix-&gt;他们在新世界中占据一席之地，从灰烬中塑造未来。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.55>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.56>legacysuffix-&gt;废墟 中团结力量的证明。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.56>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.57>legacysuffix-&gt;他们的遗产永垂不朽——铭刻在石头上，在风中低语。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.57>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.58>legacysuffix-&gt;他们的新秩序崛起，这是这片蛮荒土地上脆弱的希望。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.58>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.59>legacysuffix-&gt;他们是救世主还是怪物——但他们的影响是不可否认的。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.59>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.6>introsuffix-&gt;灰烬中诞生了新的部落、帮派和为生存而奋斗的定居点。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.6>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.7>introsuffix-&gt;从这些伤痕中诞生了羽翼未丰的社区。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.7>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.8>introsuffix-&gt;绝望的人和充满希望的人聚集在破碎的天空下闪烁的营火周围。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.8>
  <Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.9>crisis(uses=2)-&gt;他们与[place_foeLeader]领导的野蛮袭击者作战，指挥着残酷的[place_foeS老旧iers]。</Greenway_IdeoStoryPattern_General.rules.rulesStrings.9>
</LanguageData>
